      "body": "**Run 0010 T12 reconcile (r5, session 0036-horizon-T12): PASS \u2014 generic-flatness cone now fully axiom-clean.** Supersedes `I-0094` (the r4 reconcile, where the domain core was still a re-opened `sorry`).\n\n- **Kernel-verified**: `lake build` of `FlatteningStratification` + `GenericFlatnessGeometric` green (8562 jobs, exit 0). `#print axioms` on `AlgebraicGeometry.genericFlatness`, the domain core `genericallyFree_quotient_prime_of_fibre_dim_le`, and `exists_generic_rank_comparison` each report exactly `[propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound]`. No `sorry`/`admit`/`axiom` outside the 3 intended geometric leaves.\n- The r3 kernel walls (`I-0093`) were defused as claimed by extracting the generic-rank exact sequence `0 \u2192 D\u02b3 \u2192 M \u2192 T \u2192 0` into the clean-binder lemma `exists_generic_rank_comparison`; blueprint gained node `lem:generic_rank_comparison` (complete proof, `\\leanok`) and proof-`\\leanok` flipped on the domain core and both flatness theorems. Blueprint matches Lean; DAG 2201 nodes, **0 dangling**.\n- **Statement repair verified sound**: `flatLocusReduction`/`flatLocusAssembly`/`flatteningStratification`/`_universal`/`.ofCurve` strengthened `IsLocallyNoetherian \u2192 IsNoetherian`; the \u2294\u2099\ud835\udd38\u207f nested-flag counterexample genuinely defeats a finite stratification under mere local noetherianity. The \u2115-indexed `flatLocusStratification` (n=0) correctly stays locally noetherian.\n- Workspace clean (no stray files); `AJC.picrep` left `active/high` with a progress comment. Remaining T12 work is the Noetherian-induction assembly of `flatLocusReduction` and the coherent-\u03c7 substrate \u2014 neither single-session.",
